text: Heidi Mittermaier (born 28 January 1941) is a German alpine skier. She competed in two events at the 1964 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1941 births Category:Living people Category:German female alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of the United Team of Germany Category:Alpine skiers at the 1964 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Munich
